      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.nT7Vm4iuPmWBqRvQ]{Immortal Tutor (Su) - Elemental}</p>\n<p>When you cast a 1st-level or higher technomancer spell, you can gain the tutor’s first lesson for a number of rounds equal to your Intelligence modifier. After you do so, you can’t use the first lesson again until you have rested 10 minutes to regain Stamina Points.</p>\n<p><strong>First Lesson:&nbsp;</strong> You gain a special movement speed based on your patron’s type. Air grants a 20-foot fly speed (average maneuverability). Earth grants a 15-foot burrow speed. Fire grants a +20-foot enhancement bonus to your land speed. Water grants a 30-foot swim speed.</p>\n<p><em></em></p><em>\n</em><p><em>Activate relevent modifier in the Modifier tab.</em></p>"
